log
@“long double” in MirBSD (i386 and sparc, both) is currently just plain wrong and will lead to bad results; fix the code if needed
@
text
@.\"	$NetBSD: trunc.3,v 1.5 2006/04/04 20:26:33 wiz Exp $
.\"
